  "texts": [
    "Initial members could be directly appointed by the company's board of directors.",
    "But the company could also set up a special formation committee which appoints the initial board members.",
    "The former was the case at Axon's AI and Policing Technologies Ethics Board [18], the latter at Meta's Oversight Board [127].",
    "Subsequent board members are usually appointed by the board itself.",
    "Meta's Oversight Board has a special committee that selects subsequent members after a review of the candidates' qualifications and a background check [127]."
  ],
